segmentosSRT.text: Anyway, your life's worth little now.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: This case is in the way!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Whose is it? Get rid of it!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
Sir, it's mine.
I've got my things in it. Let me keep it.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Get it out of my sight then.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
It's just a bunch of puppets.
Get rid of them! This is war!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
- What are you doing?
- They're shooting!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: We're off to the next house.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: What did you think you were doing?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
- Trying to kill him, or what?
- They're just kids.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Kids? Where did he learn that from?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: This hasn't anything to do with us adults.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: We don't know what's going on.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Do you expect me to believe that?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
It's sabotage.
Sabotage to the communal kitchen.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: And sabotage of the Great Leap Forward!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: That kid could not dream that up.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
- Are you going or not?
- No!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
- I'm telling you to go!
- No!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: How do you like my singing?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
What are you doing, you little wretch?
I'll teach you a lesson!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: She smashed the windows of the jeep.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: You can't keep them. Burn them!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Erxi is good with his hands.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
Nothing compares
to the Party's benevolence
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
Chairman Mao is dearer
than father and mother
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: There's nothing as good as socialism
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: No ocean as deep as class feeling
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
Maoist Thought
is revolution's treasure trove
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Whoever opposes it, we take as our enemy
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Come on, you can't cry today.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Clear a path! Ship sailing through!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
The ship of revolution! Advance
through the storm with Chairman Mao!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: First, pay respects to Chairman Mao.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text:
Send her my very best. She's producing
a little revolutionary successor.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Dad! Mom! Has she given birth?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: But he was okay after the water.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05
